name: MSA with Missing Clauses
text:
MASTER SERVICES AGREEMENT

This Agreement is made between QuickDeal Software ("Provider") and Customer Corp. ("Customer") effective February 15, 2024.

1. SERVICES
Provider will provide software development services as described in Statements of Work.

2. TERM
This Agreement is effective for one (1) year and will automatically renew.

3. FEES
Customer shall pay [FEE AMOUNT] per month. Payment is due within [PAYMENT TERMS] of invoice.

4. INTELLECTUAL PROPERTY
Provider retains all intellectual property rights. Customer receives a license to use deliverables.

5. CONFIDENTIALITY
Both parties agree to keep confidential information confidential for [DURATION] years.

6. WARRANTIES
Provider warrants that services will be performed professionally. NO OTHER WARRANTIES ARE PROVIDED.

7. TERMINATION
Either party may terminate upon written notice.

8. GENERAL
This Agreement is the entire agreement between the parties.

[SIGNATURE BLOCK TO BE ADDED]

Provider: QuickDeal Software
Customer: Customer Corp.
